Sentencas: In this study, perovskite La0.8-xBixSr0.2FeO3-delta (LBSF, x = 0.0-0.5) nanofibers with great crystallinity were pre-pared by electrospinning method and used as cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells (ITSOFCs).
Titulo: Improved electrochemical performance of Bi doped La0.8Sr0.2FeO3-δ nanofiber cathode for IT-SOFCs via electrospinning

Sentencas: The symmetric cells of nanofiber-based LBSF electrode on Sm0.2Ce0.8O1.9 (SDC) electrolyte show excellent electrochemical performance.
Titulo: Improved electrochemical performance of Bi doped La0.8Sr0.2FeO3-δ nanofiber cathode for IT-SOFCs via electrospinning

Sentencas: The La0.4Bi0.4Sr0.2FeO3-delta (LBSF4) cathode has the best performance with a polarization resistance (RP) of 0.126 Omega cm(2) at 650 degrees C.
Titulo: Improved electrochemical performance of Bi doped La0.8Sr0.2FeO3-δ nanofiber cathode for IT-SOFCs via electrospinning

Sentencas: The anode-supported single cell with LBSF4 as the cathode film and Ni-SDC as the anode has a maximum power density of 448 mW cm(-2) at 650 degrees C using wet H-2 as the fuel.
Titulo: Improved electrochemical performance of Bi doped La0.8Sr0.2FeO3-δ nanofiber cathode for IT-SOFCs via electrospinning

Sentencas: In addition, the LBSF4 cathode with fibrous structure exhibits outstanding electrochemical behavior.
Titulo: Improved electrochemical performance of Bi doped La0.8Sr0.2FeO3-δ nanofiber cathode for IT-SOFCs via electrospinning

Sentencas: The catalytic activity of the cathode was improved due to the incorporation of the Bi element, indicating that LBSF4 is promising as a cathode material in the field of IT-SOFCs.
Titulo: Improved electrochemical performance of Bi doped La0.8Sr0.2FeO3-δ nanofiber cathode for IT-SOFCs via electrospinning
